<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ز ب د<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٢٦٣ - ز ب د]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>زبَّدَ يزبِّد، تزبيدًا، فهو مُزبِّد، والمفعول مُزبَّد <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• زبَّد اللَّبنُ:</span> علاه الزُّبْد.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• زبَّد البحرُ:</span> أزبدَ؛ دَفَع وقذف بِرَغْوته.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• زبَّد اللَّبنَ:</span> استخرج منه الزُّبْد.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>